cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language generation and uses neural networks for the same. Hence, it is likely to belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper also deals with ranking and similarity measures, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
